(1215, 1, '2016-04-20 17:21:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<p class="title">PERFECT OPPORTUNITY</p>\n<p class="body">To invest in your first home or add this great property to your investment portfolio.\nIf you are looking for a spacious home with great street appeal – this is the one!\nFeaturing 4 good sized bedrooms, the kitchen has a 900ml bi energy cooker with 5 gas burners on the top and the oven is either gas or electric along with 2 pantries, loads of bench space, a dishwasher and a stainless steel range hood.\nThe living areas are spacious, the dining is open plan off the kitchen and both areas are\nair-conditioned. The bathroom features a spa bath/shower room. The toilet is separate and laundry is spacious.\nOutside features a private covered entertainment area, a garden shed, double gate access to the yard, a double lockup carport with remote door as well as a single lockup garage with internal access to the home that is currently used as a rumpus room.\nThe location of this property is excellent, tucked away on a really private 663m2 corner allotment.</p>\nFEATURES LIST:\n4 Bedrooms, all with built-in wardrobes\nLounge with tiled floor, timber blinds, ceiling fan\nAlarm system\nTriple locks on doors and window locks on windows', '172 Brandon St, Marsden, QLD 4132', '', 'pending', 'open', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2016-04-20 17:21:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://themecss.com/wp/Homeland/?post_type=homeland_properties&amp;p=1215', 0, 'homeland_properties', '', 0),
